videos.headline: Smith-Pelly: Only halfway to what we want
videos.description: Devante Smith-Pelly explains his back-and-forth with Marc-Andre Fleury and the mood in the Caps' locker room after winning Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Smith-Pelly: Only halfway to what we want) 2018/06/02

videos.headline: Carlson: Kuznetsov 'sees the game better than anyone else'
videos.description: John Carlson details the greatness of Evgeny Kuznetsov after a stellar performance in Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Carlson: Kuznetsov 'sees the game better than anyone else') 2018/06/02

videos.headline: Good start key for Ovechkin, Capitals
videos.description: Alex Ovechkin says the Capitals are now focusing on Game 4 and discusses when he knew Evgeny Kuznetsov would play.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Good start key for Ovechkin, Capitals) 2018/06/02
